---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const siteTitle = "Urban Exploration Chronicles: Rediscovering the Past";
const siteDescription = "Documenting the hidden beauty of forgotten places. Explore abandoned buildings, ghost towns, and relics of the past. Uncover their stories.";
---

<Layout title={siteTitle} description={siteDescription}>
	<main class="container mx-auto mt-10 px-4">
		<section class="mb-8">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-accent">{siteTitle}</h1>
			<p class="text-lg">{siteDescription}</p>
			<p class="mt-4">Welcome to the Urban Exploration Chronicles, a journey into the forgotten corners of our world. Here, we document the beauty and history hidden within abandoned buildings, ghost towns, and relics of the past.</p>
			<p class="mt-4">Our mission is to uncover the stories of these places while promoting responsible and respectful exploration.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent">Photo Gallery</h2>
			<p>Explore our curated collection of high-quality photographs capturing the atmospheric essence of urban exploration.</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
				<img src="https://placehold.co/400x300.png" alt="Abandoned factory" data-ai-hint="abandoned factory interior" />
				<img src="https://placehold.co/400x300.png" alt="Ghost town street" data-ai-hint="empty street in a ghost town" />
				<img src="https://placehold.co/400x300.png" alt="Decaying architecture" data-ai-hint="close-up of decaying architecture" />
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent">Latest Blog Posts</h2>
			<p>Read detailed reports of our explorations, uncovering the history and secrets of each location.</p>
			<a href="/blog" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">View All Posts</a>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent">Exploration Map</h2>
			<p>Discover the general locations of our explorations. Note: We do not share exact coordinates to protect these sites from vandalism.</p>
			<img src="https://placehold.co/600x300.png" alt="Map of exploration areas" data-ai-hint="map showing general areas of exploration" />
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-accent">Responsible Exploration</h2>
			<p>Urban exploration can be dangerous. Always respect private property, stay safe, and leave no trace. We do not condone illegal activities.</p>
			<p class="text-red-500 font-bold">Warning: Enter at your own risk. Be aware of potential hazards such as structural instability, asbestos, and other dangers.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>